  <brief_title>Quality of Life With Esophageal Stent Trial</brief_title>
  <acronym>QUEST</acronym>
  <official_title>Prospective, Randomized Trial of the Effects on HRQoL, Cost-Utility and Reintervention Rate, of Nurse Home Visits, in Patients With SEMS Treated Malignant Disease in the Esophagus and Cardia.</official_title>
